;     RightWall     (StaticBody3D)        invisible side barrier
;       RightWallCollision (CollisionShape3D)
;
; Coordinate convention (matches main.tscn):
;   Ball travels in +Z direction.
;   Lane runs from z=0 (foul line) to z=18 (back wall).
;   Lane centred on X=0.

[gd_scene load_steps=16 format=3 uid="uid://blane001"]

